net.opentsdb.tsd

类 PipelineFactory

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.opentsdb.tsd.PipelineFactory
  • 所有已实现的接口:
    org.jboss.netty.channel.ChannelPipelineFactory

    public final class PipelineFactory
extends Object
implements org.jboss.netty.channel.ChannelPipelineFactory
    Creates a newly configured ChannelPipeline for a new channel. This class is supposed to be a singleton. NOTE: On creation (as of 2.3) the property given in the config for "tsd.core.connections.limit" will be used to limit the number of concurrent connections supported by the pipeline. The default is zero.

      • PipelineFactory

        public PipelineFactory(TSDB tsdb)
        Constructor that initializes the RPC router and loads HTTP formatter plugins. This constructor creates its own RpcManager.
        参数:
        tsdb - The TSDB to use.
        抛出:
        RuntimeException - if there is an issue loading plugins
        RuntimeException - if the HttpQuery handler is unable to load serializers

      • PipelineFactory

        public PipelineFactory(TSDB tsdb,
                       RpcManager manager)
        Constructor that initializes the RPC router and loads HTTP formatter plugins using an already-configured RpcManager.
        参数:
        tsdb - The TSDB to use.
        manager - instance of a ready-to-use RpcManager.
        抛出:
        RuntimeException - if there is an issue loading plugins throws Exception if the HttpQuery handler is unable to load serializers

      • PipelineFactory

        public PipelineFactory(TSDB tsdb,
                       RpcManager manager,
                       int connections_limit)
        Constructor that initializes the RPC router and loads HTTP formatter plugins using an already-configured RpcManager.
        参数:
        tsdb - The TSDB to use.
        manager - instance of a ready-to-use RpcManager.
        connections_limit - The maximum number of concurrent connections supported by the TSD.
        抛出:
        RuntimeException - if there is an issue loading plugins throws Exception if the HttpQuery handler is unable to load serializers
        从以下版本开始:
        2.3
